      "text": "Used for delivery of short or long acting pain or anti-spasmodic medications into the thecal space\nAllows for smaller doses and fewer systemic side effects\nMost common Intrathecal medications\nClonidine\nBupivacaine\nMorphine\nHydromorphone\nFentanyl\nBaclofen\nZiconotide",
